<div class="tab-content" id="tab-attn">
<div class="container">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Interactive Deep Dive</div>
    <h1>How Attention Works</h1>
    <p>Click a token. Watch it gather context from every other word — step by step, math made visible.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">1</div><h2>Tokenization</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><div class="tokens-row" id="tokens-row"></div><div class="explain-box"><strong>Click any token →</strong> the entire dashboard updates from that token's perspective.</div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">2</div><h2>Token Embeddings</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><div id="embedding-display" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.85rem;background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem;word-break:break-all;"></div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">3</div><h2>Why Q, K, V?</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><div class="qkv-grid"><div class="qkv-card" style="border-top:3px solid #a855f7;"><div style="color:#a855f7;font-weight:bold;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;">Q — Query</div><div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.86rem;">"What am I looking for?"</div></div><div class="qkv-card" style="border-top:3px solid #eab308;"><div style="color:#eab308;font-weight:bold;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;">K — Key</div><div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.86rem;">"What do I offer?"</div></div><div class="qkv-card" style="border-top:3px solid #10b981;"><div style="color:#10b981;font-weight:bold;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;">V — Value</div><div style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.86rem;">"Here's my actual info."</div></div></div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">4</div><h2>Computing Q, K, V Vectors</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><div id="qkv-vectors" class="qkv-grid"></div><div class="formula-box">Q = W<sub>Q</sub>·E &nbsp;|&nbsp; K = W<sub>K</sub>·E &nbsp;|&nbsp; V = W<sub>V</sub>·E</div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">5</div><h2>Attention Scores — Q·K/√d</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Focused on: <span id="scores-focused" style="color:var(--teal);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:600;"></span></p><div id="scores-bars" class="bar-list"></div><div class="explain-box" style="margin-top:1rem;">Dividing by √d = √4 = <strong>2</strong> prevents huge dot products from making softmax too sharp (gradient vanishing).</div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">6</div><h2>Softmax — Probabilities</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">Focused on: <span id="sm-focused" style="color:var(--teal);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:600;"></span></p><div id="softmax-bars" class="bar-list"></div><div class="formula-box">softmax(xᵢ) = e^xᵢ / Σ e^xⱼ</div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">7</div><h2>Attention Flow — Visual Strength Map</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.8rem;">Thicker line = stronger attention from <span id="flow-focused" style="color:var(--teal);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;"></span></p><div class="flow-vis" id="flow-vis"><svg id="flow-svg"></svg><div class="flow-tokens-row" id="flow-tokens-row"></div></div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">8</div><h2>Full Attention Matrix — Heatmap</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.8rem;">Hover to highlight. Click any cell to focus on that token.</p><div class="heatmap-wrap"><div id="heatmap" class="heatmap-grid"></div></div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">9</div><h2>Output — Contextualized Embedding</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-bottom:.8rem;">Weighted sum of all Value vectors. <span id="out-focused" style="color:var(--teal);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;"></span> is now enriched with context.</p><div id="output-display" style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:.85rem;background:rgba(0,0,0,.25);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem;word-break:break-all;"></div><div class="formula-box" style="margin-top:1rem;">output = Σ (attention_weight × V)</div></div></div>

  <!-- STEP 10 -->
  <div class="card" id="step10-card">
    <div class="card-hd">
      <div class="step-badge" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#a78bfa,#7c3aed);">10</div>
      <h2>Complete Attention Flow — Animated Visual Pipeline</h2>
      <div style="margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:.6rem;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <select id="s10-speed" style="background:var(--slate-mid);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:.28rem .5rem;border-radius:7px;font-size:.78rem;cursor:pointer;">
          <option value="2200">Normal</option><option value="1100">Fast</option><option value="3800">Slow</option>
        </select>
        <div class="focus-chip" id="s10-focus-chip">Focus: Satyam</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-bd">
      <div class="sim10-controls">
        <button class="ctrl-btn" id="s10-prev"><i class="fas fa-step-backward"></i></button>
        <button class="ctrl-btn primary" id="s10-play"><i class="fas fa-pause" id="s10-play-icon"></i></button>
        <button class="ctrl-btn" id="s10-next"><i class="fas fa-step-forward"></i></button>
        <button class="ctrl-btn" id="s10-reset" style="width:auto;padding:0 .8rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.76rem;">↺ Reset</button>
        <span id="s10-counter" style="margin-left:auto;font-size:.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);">Step 1 / 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="s10-phases" id="s10-phases"></div>
      <div class="s10-canvas" id="s10-canvas">
        <div style="color:var(--text-dim);text-align:center;padding:2rem;">Loading...</div>
      </div>
      <div class="s10-explain" id="s10-explain">
        <div class="s10-explain-icon" id="s10-icon">⚡</div>
        <div class="s10-explain-text" id="s10-text">Press Play or click a phase to begin the attention animation.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">11</div><h2>From Attention to LLM</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><div class="llm-grid"><div class="llm-card"><div class="llm-card-icon">🏗️</div><strong>96 Layers</strong><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;">GPT-4 stacks attention blocks 96× deep.</div></div><div class="llm-card"><div class="llm-card-icon">🧠</div><strong>Multi-Head</strong><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;">8–96 Q,K,V sets in parallel. Each head finds different patterns.</div></div><div class="llm-card"><div class="llm-card-icon">⚡</div><strong>Feed-Forward</strong><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;">Neural net processes each position after attention.</div></div><div class="llm-card"><div class="llm-card-icon">🔗</div><strong>Residuals</strong><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-top:.3rem;">E' = E + Attention(E). Prevents vanishing gradients.</div></div></div><div class="formula-box" style="margin-top:1rem;">Attention(Q,K,V) = softmax(QKᵀ/√d) × V</div></div></div>
  <div class="card"><div class="card-hd"><div class="step-badge">12</div><h2>How Q&A and Reasoning Work</h2></div><div class="card-bd"><p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;line-height:1.7;">LLMs don't "understand" — they predict the next token based on learned patterns.</p><div class="qkv-grid"><div class="qkv-card" style="border-left:4px solid #f87171;"><div style="color:#f87171;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;">Direct Answering</div><div style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.6;">Question → Answer<br><em>Hard jump. Often fails on complex tasks.</em></div></div><div class="qkv-card" style="border-left:4px solid #34d399;"><div style="color:#34d399;font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:.4rem;">Chain-of-Thought</div><div style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.6;">Question → Step 1 → Step 2 → Answer<br><em>Each step becomes context. Much stronger.</em></div></div></div><div class="explain-box" style="margin-top:1rem;"><strong>This is why prompting matters.</strong> Structure your prompt well and the model pattern-matches to higher quality training sequences.</div></div></div>
</div>
