      <p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.6;">MCP is like <strong>USB-C for AI tools</strong>. Instead of every AI app needing custom integrations for every tool, MCP provides one universal protocol. Built by Anthropic, adopted by OpenAI, LangChain, and others.</p>
